    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at this risk level per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The output comparison factor is assessed at Gradation 2 based on CFD benchmark comparison; the assessment team concluded that the numerical reference dataset, having been correlated with PIV data in a prior independent study, provides equivalent evidentiary support to direct experimental measurement. The relative hemolysis index is below the RH < 1.0 acceptance threshold at all five operating points. The package is accepted for regulatory submission.",
